<div type="content"><del rend="crossout"><ab facs="#facs_483_r2l11"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> . Als vns ewr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> <expan>yecʒ<ex>unden</ex></expan>
