<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan></del> / vnd ſein oncʒweyfel ee <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden dıſer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_483_r2l27"> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> brief werde . Eʒ hab 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan></del> . der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
